WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:04.500
UX Designer prompt: Design the UX for the feedback widget.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:08.500
AgentX sketches a low fidelity wireframe.

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:27.000
The wireframe shows a dismissible widget with three sentiment options, optional comment, and a screenshot toggle.

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:48.000
The wireframe transitions into a live H T M L prototype, validated by axe-core. Zero accessibility violations. W C A G 2.1 A A pass.

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:53.500
Wireframe to prototype in fifty eight seconds. Mobile and desktop variants. Audit report committed.

00:00:54.000 --> 00:01:00.000
From prompt to accessible prototype. Powered by ux-designer dot agent dot m d.
